  "intent": "Run a DNA extraction from blood samples using the magnetic beads method. First add some starting buffer, then lysis buffer to break open the cells and mix everything up. Let it sit for a bit, then use the magnet to pull down the beads with DNA stuck to them. Wash the beads a bunch of times to get rid of all the junk, then heat everything up and add elution buffer to get the clean DNA off the beads. Finally move the purified DNA to a fresh plate for whatever comes next.",
